<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="Déployez une plateforme d'automatisation Ansible complète en 15 minutes. AWX, Gitea, PKI, monitoring — tout intégré. Sans comptage de nœuds." />
  <title>Autoflow — L'automatisation enterprise. Sans la complexité.</title>
  <style>
    /* ── Reset ── */
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --bg:        #0a0a0f;
      --bg2:       #111118;
      --bg3:       #1a1a24;
      --bg4:       #22222e;
      --border:    #2a2a3a;
      --accent:    #6c63ff;
      --accent2:   #a78bfa;
      --accent3:   #38bdf8;
      --green:     #22c55e;
      --text:      #e2e8f0;
      --text-dim:  #94a3b8;
      --text-muted:#64748b;
      --font:      'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      --font-mono: 'Fira Code', 'Cascadia Code', 'Courier New', monospace;
      --radius:    10px;
      --radius-lg: 16px;
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font);
           font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; overflow-x: hidden; }
    a { color: var(--accent2); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    /* ── Noise overlay ── */
    body::before {
      content: ''; position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.03'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      opacity: .4;
    }

    /* ── Nav ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 40px; height: 64px;
      background: rgba(10,10,15,.85); backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; color: var(--text); }
    .nav-logo .logo-icon {
      width: 32px; height: 32px; background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 8px; display: grid; place-items: center; font-size: 16px;
    }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; }
    .nav-links a { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 500; transition: color .2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .nav-cta { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 9px 20px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: all .2s; border: none;
    }
    .btn-ghost { background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-dim); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--text); }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent); color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(108,99,255,.35);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent2); box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(108,99,255,.5); transform: translateY(-1px); }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      position: relative; min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
      justify-content: center; text-align: center; padding: 120px 40px 80px;
    }
    .hero-glow {
      position: absolute; top: 20%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 800px; height: 400px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(108,99,255,.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(108,99,255,.1); border: 1px solid rgba(108,99,255,.3);
      padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--accent2); margin-bottom: 28px; font-weight: 500;
    }
    .hero-badge .dot-pulse {
      width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--green);
      box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--green); animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;} 50%{opacity:.4;} }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 72px); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -.03em; margin-bottom: 24px; position: relative;
    }
    .hero h1 .grad {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 30%, var(--accent2));
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px); color: var(--text-dim);
      max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 40px; line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .hero p strong { color: var(--text); }
    .hero-buttons { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 56px; }
    .btn-large { padding: 14px 28px; font-size: 15px; border-radius: 10px; }
    .hero-trust { display: flex; gap: 32px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .trust-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dim); }
    .trust-item .icon { color: var(--green); font-size: 15px; }

    /* ── Terminal ── */
    .terminal-wrap { position: relative; margin: 60px auto 0; max-width: 680px; }
    .terminal {
      background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.6), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.04);
    }
    .terminal-bar {
      background: var(--bg3); padding: 12px 16px; display: flex;
      align-items: center; gap: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .tbar-dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; }
    .tbar-dot.r { background: #ff5f57; } .tbar-dot.y { background: #febc2e; } .tbar-dot.g { background: #28c840; }
    .tbar-title { flex: 1; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); font-family: var(--font-mono); }
    .terminal-body { padding: 20px 24px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.9; }
    .t-prompt { color: var(--accent2); }
    .t-cmd    { color: var(--text); }
    .t-ok     { color: var(--green); }
    .t-arrow  { color: var(--accent); }
    .t-url    { color: var(--accent3); }
    .t-dim    { color: var(--text-muted); }
    .t-time   { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }

    /* ── Stats bar ── */
    .stats-bar {
      display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 60px; flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 40px; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 800px;
    }
    .stat { text-align: center; }
    .stat .val { font-size: 40px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent2);
                 letter-spacing: -.03em; display: block; }
    .stat .lbl { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 4px; }

    /* ── Section ── */
    .section { padding: 100px 40px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-label {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent2);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .12em; margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .section h2 {
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px); font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -.02em; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .section h2 span { color: var(--accent2); }
    .section > .sub {
      font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-dim); max-width: 540px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 56px;
    }
    .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 0; }

    /* ── Feature Grid ── */
    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
    .feature-card {
      background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 28px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      transition: border-color .2s, transform .2s;
    }
    .feature-card:hover { border-color: rgba(108,99,255,.5); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .feature-card::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: 0; transition: opacity .3s;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 60% 20%, rgba(108,99,255,.06), transparent 60%);
    }
    .feature-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 10px; display: grid;
      place-items: center; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;
      background: rgba(108,99,255,.12); border: 1px solid rgba(108,99,255,.2);
    }
    .feature-card h3 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .feature-card p  { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .feature-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
    .feature-list li { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dim); display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; }
    .feature-list li::before { content: '✓'; color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

    /* ── Comparison table ── */
    .comparison-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
    .comparison-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; }
    .comparison-table th {
      padding: 16px 20px; text-align: left; background: var(--bg2);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border); font-weight: 700;
    }
    .comparison-table th.highlight { color: var(--accent2); }
    .comparison-table td {
      padding: 14px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--text-dim);
    }
    .comparison-table tr:hover td { background: var(--bg2); }
    .comparison-table td.highlight { font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
    .check { color: var(--green); font-size: 16px; }
    .cross { color: #475569; font-size: 16px; }
    .partial { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 13px; }

    /* ── Pricing ── */
    .pricing-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
    .pricing-card {
      background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 32px; position: relative;
    }
    .pricing-card.popular {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(108,99,255,.2);
    }
    .popular-badge {
      position: absolute; top: -13px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: var(--accent); color: #fff; padding: 4px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .pricing-tier { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent2);
                    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .1em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .pricing-price { font-size: 40px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -.03em;
                     margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .pricing-price .period { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 400; }
    .pricing-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .pricing-divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 20px 0; }
    .pricing-features { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .pricing-features li { font-size: 14px; display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .pricing-features li::before { content: '✓'; color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .pricing-features li.disabled { color: var(--text-muted); }
    .pricing-features li.disabled::before { content: '–'; color: var(--text-muted); }

    /* ── CTA Banner ── */
    .cta-banner {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(108,99,255,.12) 0%, rgba(56,189,248,.08) 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(108,99,255,.25); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 64px 40px; text-align: center; margin: 0 40px;
    }
    .cta-banner h2 { font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 42px); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: -.02em; }
    .cta-banner p  { font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 560px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .cta-note { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .cta-note span { margin: 0 8px; }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    footer {
      background: var(--bg2); border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 60px 40px 32px; margin-top: 80px;
    }
    .footer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px;
                   max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto 48px; }
    .footer-brand p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-dim); margin: 12px 0 20px; max-width: 260px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .footer-col h4 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
                     letter-spacing: .1em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .footer-col ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .footer-col ul li a { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-dim); transition: color .2s; }
    .footer-col ul li a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .footer-bottom {
      max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: gap;
    }
    .footer-bottom p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
    .footer-links a { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    /* ── Served by badge ── */
    .served-by {
      position: fixed; bottom: 16px; right: 16px; z-index: 50;
      background: var(--bg3); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
    }
    .served-by span { color: var(--green); }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav { padding: 0 20px; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero { padding: 100px 20px 60px; }
      .stats-bar { gap: 32px; padding: 32px 20px; }
      .section { padding: 60px 20px; }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .cta-banner { margin: 0 20px; padding: 40px 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-logo">
      <div class="logo-icon">⚡</div>
      Autoflow
    </div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#features">Fonctionnalités</a>
      <a href="#comparison">vs AAP</a>
      <a href="#pricing">Tarifs</a>
      <a href="#blog">Blog</a>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-cta">
      <a href="https://github.com/getautoflow/autoflow" class="btn btn-ghost">Community</a>
      <a href="https://getautoflow.dev/demo" class="btn btn-primary">Réserver une démo</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-glow"></div>

    <div class="hero-badge">
      <span class="dot-pulse"></span>
      Déployé par Ansible sur {{ ansible_distribution }} {{ ansible_distribution_version }}
    </div>

    <h1>
      L'automatisation Ansible<br/>
      <span class="grad">sans la complexité.</span>
    </h1>

    <p>
      Déployez une plateforme d'automatisation enterprise complète en <strong>15 minutes</strong>.
      AWX, PKI, observabilité — tout intégré. Gérez 10 ou 10&nbsp;000 nœuds <strong>au même prix</strong>.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-buttons">
      <a href="https://getautoflow.dev/demo" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">
        Réserver une démo →
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/getautoflow/autoflow" class="btn btn-ghost btn-large">
        Version Community
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-trust">
      <div class="trust-item"><span class="icon">✓</span> Aucun comptage de nœuds</div>
      <div class="trust-item"><span class="icon">✓</span> Données 100% sur vos serveurs</div>
      <div class="trust-item"><span class="icon">✓</span> Fonctionne hors ligne</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Terminal -->
    <div class="terminal-wrap">
      <div class="terminal">
        <div class="terminal-bar">
          <div class="tbar-dot r"></div>
          <div class="tbar-dot y"></div>
          <div class="tbar-dot g"></div>
          <div class="tbar-title">Deploy Wizard — Autoflow</div>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body">
          <div><span class="t-prompt">$ </span><span class="t-cmd">make wizard</span></div>
          <div class="t-dim">Autoflow Deploy Wizard → :9000</div>
          <div>&nbsp;</div>
          <div><span class="t-ok">✓</span> Domain configured <span class="t-url">client.example.com</span></div>
          <div><span class="t-ok">✓</span> Secrets generated</div>
          <div><span class="t-ok">✓</span> PKI &amp; wildcard cert created</div>
          <div><span class="t-ok">✓</span> Critical volumes ready</div>
          <div><span class="t-ok">✓</span> Stack deployed — <span class="t-time">14m 32s</span></div>
          <div>&nbsp;</div>
          <div><span class="t-arrow">→</span> AWX      <span class="t-url">https://awx.client.example.com</span></div>
          <div><span class="t-arrow">→</span> Gitea    <span class="t-url">https://git.client.example.com</span></div>
          <div><span class="t-arrow">→</span> Grafana  <span class="t-url">https://monitoring.client.example.com</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="val">14m</span>
      <div class="lbl">Temps de déploiement</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="val">5×</span>
      <div class="lbl">Moins cher qu'AAP</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="val">∞</span>
      <div class="lbl">Nœuds gérés</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="val">100%</span>
      <div class="lbl">On-premise</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <!-- FEATURES -->
  <section class="section" id="features">
    <div class="section-label">⚡ Fonctionnalités</div>
    <h2>Tout ce dont vous avez besoin.<br/><span>Rien de superflu.</span></h2>
    <p class="sub">Autoflow intègre chaque brique de l'automatisation enterprise dans une stack cohérente, testée, documentée.</p>

    <div class="features-grid">

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🚀</div>
        <h3>Déploiement en 15 minutes</h3>
        <p>Le wizard interactif guide chaque étape : domaine, certificats, secrets, services. Pas un seul fichier YAML à éditer.</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Interface web sur :9000 — aucune CLI requise</li>
          <li>Génération automatique des secrets et de la PKI</li>
          <li>Déploiement idempotent et reproductible</li>
          <li>Support air-gap : toutes les images peuvent être mirrorées</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
        <h3>Observabilité complète</h3>
        <p>Grafana, Prometheus, Loki et Tempo pré-configurés. Dashboards opérationnels sans une ligne de configuration.</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Dashboards AWX, système et applicatifs préconfigurés</li>
          <li>Logs centralisés dans Loki, traces dans Tempo</li>
          <li>Alerting Prometheus avec routes par équipe</li>
          <li>Rétention et archivage via MinIO intégré</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
        <h3>Sécurité &amp; PKI</h3>
        <p>Autoflow génère une CA privée et des certificats wildcard en 60 secondes. Vos services internes restent HTTPS.</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>CA interne X.509, certificats wildcard par domaine</li>
          <li>Renouvellement automatique des certificats</li>
          <li>Compatibilité air-gap totale (pas de ACME externe)</li>
          <li>Vault-ready pour les secrets à long terme</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🗂️</div>
        <h3>SCM intégré (Gitea)</h3>
        <p>Un dépôt Git privé intégré pour stocker vos playbooks, rôles et inventaires. Synchronisation native avec AWX.</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Gitea auto-configuré et connecté à AWX</li>
          <li>Webhooks pour déclenchement automatique</li>
          <li>Gestion RBAC multi-équipes</li>
          <li>Miroir de dépôts externes possible</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🌐</div>
        <h3>Multi-site &amp; Air-gap</h3>
        <p>Conçu pour les environnements isolés. Toutes les images Docker peuvent être mirrorées localement.</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Déploiements multi-sites centralisés</li>
          <li>Registre Docker privé inclus</li>
          <li>Pas de dépendance internet en production</li>
          <li>Compatible réseaux classifiés et OT</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">💰</div>
        <h3>Prix prévisible</h3>
        <p>Zéro comptage de nœuds. Zéro module payant. Vous savez exactement ce que vous payez chaque année.</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Forfait annuel fixe, nœuds illimités</li>
